summary: DROG: The Meme Coin Hybrid Leading the Neiro Era! - As we honor Kabosu, the Shiba Inu behind Dogecoin, we embrace Neiro, the new face of meme culture. Now, get ready for DROG to lead this wild new era. DROG is the surreal hybrid poised to become the next meme coin legend. Missed out on Pepe, Doge, and Neiro? Don’t make the same mistake again. DROG is not just another coin; it’s the embodiment of internet humor and bizarre creativity, ready to take the world by storm. Leading the Neiro Era with a ribbit, a bark, and a lot of sass, DROG is set to join the pantheon of meme icons.
